{"tid":2027533,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思广益] 想换輛国产车，求推介","createTime":"2020-05-21T12:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T10:35:57.000Z","uid":147916,"like":87,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"cc8c221bce0932aeaddda19d5df43c0d0ffe216e","tid":2027533,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:05:53.000Z","msg":"为表示我是一个爱国爱党，有高尚情操的中国人<br />\n我决定不再驾驶洋鬼子的汽车，买輛国产车身体力行支持袓国繁荣发展<br />\n现在想听听各位见识广博的连登巴打意见<br />\n我对汽车的要求不高，能装得下习大大便可以<br />\n以防将来有天习大大访港我可以亲手接待他带他游走香港省<br />\n颜色方面最好有好红色，越红越好，这样才能显出我爱国的心<br />\n心急人在线等。。。"},{"pid":"c2e6db9616ab8df841cd2c586b6e1ba1ed9525f0","tid":2027533,"uid":204106,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"同志 买BYD吧"},{"pid":"7b4b95ae00effdb4c10223ea858554b79b2b3e8b","tid":2027533,"uid":147916,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:07:43.000Z","msg":"怎么一个回应也没有？<br />\n连登讨论区不是一个爱国讨论区来吗？<br />\n如果没有人回应的话我还是回去微博吧。 。 。"},{"pid":"4e7ebae9e034984d83afc4e998e4e80fb830cd7b","tid":2027533,"uid":333287,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndfqiLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndfqiLA.jpg&h=d41287b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bad8d390af723d7fb16577d9fc07b1a940c52b9","tid":2027533,"uid":119232,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"車本身就係西方產物<br />\n建議騎馬"},{"pid":"9b4b2f5e483f97d10884bb0b0d44d8e01d6e3ab0","tid":2027533,"uid":147916,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"c2e6db9616ab8df841cd2c586b6e1ba1ed9525f0","tid":2027533,"uid":204106,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"同志 买BYD吧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"这个品牌怎样读？<br />\n你为何跟我说洋文？<br />\n难度你是汉奸？"},{"pid":"1a60ab35ee0280fbc71ba0fd678a0d3c8a7de23b","tid":2027533,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike"